1. Go to https://marg.dabur.com.np
2. Click Report
3. Click Dabur Report and then SKU Report.
4. After downloading, you need to remove some lines from the excel.

For eg from Row 1 to row 5.
{sku-report
CompanyName : Dabur Central
VATNO: 123456789
ADDRESS: Kathmandu
@ReportType: MTD @Daterange from : 01-01-2026 To 01-30-2026 @Mode: Salesman Wise -Detail}

5. Upload the excel
6. TADAAAAA your Weekly Report is ready.

ENJOY!!! 
